'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #3003] on 20 November 2000 at 8:22:30 am'!!Morph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'di 11/20/2000 08:20'!fullDrawOn: aCanvas	"Draw the full Morphic structure on the given Canvas"	self visible ifFalse: [^ self].	(self hasProperty: #errorOnDraw) ifTrue:[^self drawErrorOn: aCanvas].	"Note: At some point we should generalize this into some sort of 	multi-canvas so that we can cross-optimize some drawing operations."	"Pass 1: Draw eventual drop-shadow"	self hasDropShadow ifTrue: [self drawDropShadowOn: aCanvas].	(self hasRolloverBorder and: [(aCanvas seesNothingOutside: self bounds) not])		ifTrue: [self drawRolloverBorderOn: aCanvas].	"Pass 2: Draw receiver itself"	aCanvas roundCornersOf: self during:[		aCanvas drawMorph: self.		self drawSubmorphsOn:aCanvas.		self drawDropHighlightOn: aCanvas.		self drawMouseDownHighlightOn: aCanvas].! !